  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2025-10-23 18:13</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p>多模态指令驱动的编辑和生成模型DreamOmni2，潜在扩散模型SVG，量化模型olmOCR-2，方法R-HORIZON，完全自主框架Socratic-Zero，自动生成演讲视频Paper2Video，</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eefe0b80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAtofFwPUoz9FKiavicEzicTjldIksu8fK62myEbkrB3z4TzZY1aCnxfRdnSg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DreamOmni2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"604\" data-imgfileid=\"100016311\" data-ratio=\"0.5148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1174\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f51ed9d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAtoISf5KgvVM7WPRBsq4kgtCPsGQOcCKs5OxhCC4zA8BpscSCtoIbCicnw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DreamOmni2 是一个多模态指令驱动的编辑和生成模型。它在传统的基于具体对象的生成任务中表现优异，尤其在身份和姿态一致性方面。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型还支持抽象属性的引用，如材质、纹理、化妆、发型、设计风格等，甚至在某些方面超越了商业模型。此外，DreamOmni2 还支持多模态指令编辑，能够处理需要参考图像的编辑任务。总体而言，DreamOmni2 是一个更智能、更强大的开源统一生成和编辑模型，适用于广泛的任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dreamomni2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dreamomni2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：SVG</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"368\" data-imgfileid=\"100016314\" data-ratio=\"0.3138888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1172\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=13f97e8c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAto9TZUhZPz9wcksgFiaf2JoPbtIvIaGwzX8N2KTYRh3bc4v3NY8169mcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SVG是一个新颖的潜在扩散模型，不依赖变分自动编码器，旨在释放自监督表示用于视觉生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目的核心组件包括</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">SVG自动编码器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">潜在扩散变压器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。SVG自动编码器使用冻结的表示编码器和残差分支来补偿信息损失，并通过学习的卷积解码器将SVG潜在空间转换为像素空间。潜在扩散变压器则直接在SVG潜在空间上执行扩散建模。项目提供了PyTorch实现的SVG自动编码器和潜在扩散变压器，并支持端到端训练和采样脚本以及多GPU分布式训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/svg-shiml20-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/svg-shiml20-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：olmOCR-2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"514\" data-imgfileid=\"100016310\" data-ratio=\"0.4398148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38cf6f49&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAtoSYgBzVn9ZlCVm1Q7jWBLLaFtelUCg9QUQray6u5Rjhx9CiaFxicfrcvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★olmOCR-2-7B-1025-FP8 是一个经过量化的版本，基于 Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct 微调而成，使用 olmOCR-mix-1025 数据集进行训练。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过 GRPO RL 训练进一步提升了在数学公式、表格和其他复杂 OCR 场景下的性能。它是一个高效的文档识别工具，能够将大量文档转换为纯文本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/olmocr-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/olmocr-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：R-HORIZON</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"668\" data-imgfileid=\"100016312\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1172\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1b3246c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAtoliaVcd0IN2ft0WTwfLTdSRonKUKIqCOUOwNyB25Dy4rytAIfnd5qFzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★R-HORIZON 是一种新颖的方法，旨在通过查询组合来激发大规模推理模型（LRMs）的长期推理行为。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目将孤立的问题转化为复杂的多步推理场景，揭示了即使是最先进的LRMs在面对跨越长推理范围的相互依赖问题时也会出现显著的性能下降。R-HORIZON 通过引入一个包含数学、代码生成和Agent应用的6个代表性数据集的基准，解决了现有基准测试范围有限、有效推理长度有限和思维预算分配不当等问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/r-horizon\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/r-horizon</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Socratic-Zero</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"100016313\" data-ratio=\"0.6166666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f1b5fbd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAtozpfQNc2E0pIuG1HF3FSZNQRODlAKZNuKsY6k2icfniaJlNibkYIkxMytg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Socratic-Zero 是一个完全自主的框架，通过教师、求解器和生成器三个代理的共进化，从最小的种子示例生成高质量的数学推理训练数据。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该方法从仅100个种子问题开始，不依赖于大量的外部数据集，便能实现显著的性能提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/socratic-zero\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/socratic-zero</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Paper2Video</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"418\" data-imgfileid=\"100016315\" data-ratio=\"0.35833333333333334\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21b7eaf7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwYdMHJcicIJWesUNunNOAtoz1eoiax4xnlVBvREXvua1AdIVYXRJXKbTuAriaicJ77VrTWhycO8rod4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Paper2Video项目旨在从学术论文中自动生成演讲视频，通过输入一篇论文、一张图片和一段音频，该项目能够生成一段完整的演讲视频。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目的核心是PaperTalker，一个集成了幻灯片、字幕、光标定位、语音合成和演讲者视频渲染的智能代理。Paper2Video还提供了一个基准，用于评估演讲视频的质量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/paper2video01\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/paper2video01</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100012181\" data-ratio=\"1.5712962962962962\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=050dd75e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzsuveu0Oib7RPoas9iaReIDLd72zAJkrNOCp7A0IRgbeicADqBSicz36BLdGh2dz1C7E5PZgibCqFNSRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"107\" data-imgfileid=\"100013546\" data-ratio=\"0.18518518518518517\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);letter-spacing: 0.578px;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73250edd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky46ibiaDkwPpOl085OGW8JMM572LKqicN8ordMGb1lKKwclv8NbFEOlFRqAojINufXDNiaERbIkUv8EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></span><span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <p><strong style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2247499975\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=ce34959b&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzkyMzcwMDIyMQ%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247499975%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D7a94aa3b7fc72816c25bc66d5b09e1c4\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总介绍了 2025 年 10 月 23 日发布的多个开源多模态模型、潜在扩散模型、量化 OCR 模型、AI 长期推理方法及 Agent 框架，涵盖统一生成、编辑、文档识别、视频生成等前沿技术。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总介绍了 2025 年 10 月 23 日发布的多个开源多模态模型、潜在扩散模型、量化 OCR 模型、AI 长期推理方法及 Agent 框架，涵盖统一生成、编辑、文档识别、视频生成等前沿技术。",
  "summary": "本文作为“今日开源”栏目，精选并介绍了 2025 年 10 月 23 日发布的六个前沿开源项目。在“基座模型”部分，重点介绍了 DreamOmni2，一个多模态指令驱动的生成与编辑模型，其在身份姿态一致性及抽象属性引用方面表现出色；SVG，一个不依赖变分自动编码器的新型潜在扩散模型，利用自监督表示进行视觉生成；以及 olmOCR-2，一个基于 Qwen2.5-VL-7B 微调的量化 OCR 模型，专为复杂文档识别优化。在“框架平台、必备工具”部分，R-HORIZON 提出了一种通过查询组合激发大规模推理模型（LRMs）长期推理行为的新方法，并提供了新的基准测试；Socratic-Zero 则是一个完全自主的框架，通过代理共进化从少量种子示例生成高质量数学推理训练数据。最后，“Agent 开发”部分介绍了 Paper2Video，一个能从学术论文自动生成演讲视频的智能代理项目。文章旨在为技术从业者提供最新的开源 AI 技术动态和项目速览，帮助他们快速了解并发现前沿创新。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "DreamOmni2 开源多模态模型在身份姿态一致性及抽象属性引用上实现突破。",
      "explanation": "该模型通过多模态指令驱动，统一处理图像生成与编辑任务，有效解决了传统模型在保持主体一致性方面的难题，并支持对材质、纹理等抽象属性的精细控制，超越了部分商业模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "文章聚合了 AI 模型、推理方法和 Agent 框架等多个领域的最新开源进展。",
      "explanation": "通过 SVG（新型潜在扩散模型）、olmOCR-2（高效量化 OCR）、R-HORIZON（长期推理方法）和 Paper2Video（AI Agent 自动视频生成）等多样化项目，为 AI 从业者提供了丰富的技术动态和研究方向。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Socratic-Zero 框架通过代理共进化，自主生成高质量数学推理训练数据。",
      "explanation": "该方法仅需少量种子示例，便能通过教师、求解器和生成器三个代理的协同进化，实现高质量数学推理训练数据的自主扩充，显著提升大规模推理模型在复杂任务上的性能。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "DreamOmni2 是一个更智能、更强大的开源统一生成和编辑模型，适用于广泛的任务。",
